    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2011 Porsche 911 Carrera S (997.2) represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated driver engagement. Featuring the 3.8L MA101 flat-six engine with Direct Fuel Injection, this unit delivers 385 hp with a linear power band and a visceral 7,500 RPM redline. The 6-speed manual transaxle offers short, precise throws, complemented by a factory-optioned limited-slip differential and Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) for optimized damping. The chassis remains exceptionally stiff, showing zero signs of fatigue. Meticulously maintained with a documented service history, the DME report confirms zero over-revs in critical ranges. This example sits on staggered forged alloys wrapped in fresh Michelin Pilot Sport 4S rubber, ensuring peak mechanical grip. The exterior finish and interior upholstery are in museum-quality state, free of any structural or cosmetic degradation.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
