    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting an absolute time capsule: a flawlessly maintained specimen in showroom condition. The exterior retains its original factory paint with a deep, mirror-like luster, entirely free of rock chips, swirl marks, or imperfections. Every body panel is laser-straight with perfect gaps. Inside, the cabin remains pristine; the leather is supple with no bolster wear, the carpets are spotless, and it retains that distinct new-car aroma. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the climate control, operates with precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having been exclusively serviced at authorized intervals with a comprehensive binder of maintenance records included. The engine bay is concours-level clean, and the undercarriage is immaculate, reflecting its history in a climate-controlled garage. This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade vehicle that looks, feels, and drives exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line.",
